    <item>
      <title>东德选民使梅尔斯计划促进乌克兰防御的计划复杂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/east-german-voters-complicate-merz-plan-to-boost-ukraine-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里斯蒂安·戈尔克（ChristianGörke）不反对德国放松其借贷规则，而是不希望“对军备业的纯粹经济刺激”。这位资深左派立法者是新的议员阶级的一部分，该阶级将于下个月到达联邦议员，形成反对即将上任的基督教民主总理弗里德里希·梅尔斯（Friedrich Merz）的强有力的反对派。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/east-german-voters-complicate-merz-plan-to-boost-ukraine-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯准备削减支出计划，以遵守财政规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/reeves-ready-to-slash-spending-plans-to-stay-within-fiscal-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）正准备削减她的支出计划并要求公共部门提高其糟糕的生产力，因为英国的国库总理试图修复政府财务状况的漏洞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/reeves-ready-to-slash-spending-plans-to-stay-within-fiscal-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联社说，联邦工人开始收到新的电子邮件以证明工作是合理的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/federal-workers-start-getting-new-email-to-justify-job-ap-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联社报道，美国联邦工人再次收到一封电子邮件，要求他们概述自己的成就，这次是一条消息，即每周发生一次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/federal-workers-start-getting-new-email-to-justify-job-ap-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 05:05:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将于下周五在白宫举办加密峰会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/trump-will-host-crypto-summit-at-the-white-house-next-friday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统将在下周五主持白宫首次加密货币峰会，进一步确立了他对该行业的拥护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/trump-will-host-crypto-summit-at-the-white-house-next-friday</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 02:50:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Yoon的弹each判决临近，韩国人集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/south-koreans-to-rally-as-yoon-s-impeachment-verdict-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从Yoon Suk Yeol总统因其戒严宣言而弹each以来，成千上万的韩国人将在首尔聚集在首尔，因为法官进入了他们是否确认他的罢免还是恢复他的审议的最后一段时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/south-koreans-to-rally-as-yoon-s-impeachment-verdict-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 00:18:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
