      <title>澳大利亚的绿色眼睛记录禁令是选举国王的角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/australia-s-greens-eye-logging-ban-in-role-as-election-kingmaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果即将举行的联邦选举结束而没有明显的赢家，澳大利亚的绿党将要求在本地森林中登录，并邀请该党加入工党政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/australia-s-greens-eye-logging-ban-in-role-as-election-kingmaker</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 23:50:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官呼叫司法部关于马斯克·马克（Musk Doge）角色“高度可疑”的回答</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/judge-calls-doj-answers-about-musk-doge-role-highly-suspicious</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名负责监督诉讼的联邦法官声称埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）正在发挥巨大的违宪权力来重塑美国政府，他说他对特朗普政府对亿万富翁的实际角色的不完整解释“非常可疑”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/judge-calls-doj-answers-about-musk-doge-role-highly-suspicious</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 23:10:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
